  System Requirements
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  - Linux 32/64Bit
  - Digitizer X730/ x725 family with DAW firmware

  How to get support
  ------------------
  CAEN makes available the technical support of its specialists for requests
  concerning CAEN products. Use the support form available at the following link:
  https://www.caen.it/support-services/support-form


  Description:
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Add two functions:
  1. Fixed-duration data taking
     add 'ACQ_TIME' paramter in DAW_Config.txt, following by a int type number unit of Second, with syntax
     ACQ_TIME  [time length]

  2. Print RunStart time and Duration in the tail of rawdata file,  like:
     /mnt/data/PMT/R8520_406/daq_acq_time_raw_b0_file0_20250916_193019_338_10s.bin
     

  Syntax
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  DAW_Demo [config file]

  
  DAW_Demo config_2board_sync.txt